videos.headline: Buffalo strikes first
videos.description: Tyree Jackson's 14-yard run for a touchdown gives Buffalo a 7-0 lead.

videos.headline: Buffalo extends the lead to 14
videos.description: Tyree Jackson and Anthony Johnson connect from 14 yards out give the Bulls a 14-point lead.

videos.headline: Buffalo scores again
videos.description: Emmanuel Reed scores from 10-yards out to widen the margin for Buffalo.

videos.headline: Buffalo dominating Colgate
videos.description: Johnathan Hawkins scores his first touchdown of the game from 1-yard out to further the lead for Buffalo.

videos.headline: Colgate gets their first touchdown
videos.description: Malik Twyman runs it in from 5-yards out to cut into the Buffalo lead.
